  "detailed_description": "Racer 8 is the ultimate Rally inspired puzzle game that will have players revving their engines or leave them running on fumes!<br />\r\nA mixture of asset management, time trial and puzzle game, Racer 8 plays on several different mechanics to keep players’ heads constantly spinning.<br />\r\nNavigate your car, which is constantly in motion while rotate the square tiles on the map grid in order to form a track for your car to follow, through a series of checkpoints and ultimately across the finish line.",
